## TypeOf type

Obtains the TypeScript type of the given runtime Type-checker. Aka [The](./types.the.md)<!-- -->.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type TypeOf<T> = T extends TypeLink<infer Q> ? Q : never;
```
